This is just an explanation of the files present on the folder:



functions.h ---------- header file with function declaration
globals.h ------------ declaration of variables across callbacks
globalsE.h ----------- declaration of variables across callbacks in an external manner
                       useful for easy access to the globals for each .c file

interface.h ---------- functions to create windows
interface.c

main.c --------------- Hello World! :-P

support.h ------------ automated files generated by glade
support.c

callbacks.c ---------- callbacks of the main window
callbacks_draw.c ----- callbacks related to drawing in the main window
callbacks_menu.c ----- main window menu
callbacks_ascEdit.c -- for the edition of the asc files